 />\n康熙辭典都唔信我野好講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好無說服力喎<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/29/133633_24c08bd75b3b11486d573771ce1cc929.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F29%2F133633_24c08bd75b3b11486d573771ce1cc929.jpg&h=84f15855&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbc2d71f10dbe094466b29dbf03fe4eb447e043f","tid":58538,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T05:38:28.000Z","msg":"轉貼：<br />\n<br />\n「鍾意」是廣東話, 意思是喜歡, 愛. 書面語無此詞語. 但查辭典(台灣教育部國語辭典 http://140.111.1.22/mandr/clc/dict): <br />\n<br />\n「鍾愛」 = 特別疼愛。[北史˙卷十二˙隋煬帝本紀：上美姿儀，少敏慧，高祖及后於諸子中，特所鍾愛。三國演義˙第十六回：惟嚴氏生一女，布最鍾愛。] <br />\n<br />\n「鍾情」 = 專情愛慕。如：一見鍾情。 <br />\n<br />\n至於「中意」, 也是一個正確的書面語, 意思係合意、滿意。[漢書˙卷四十五˙江充傳：奉法不阿，所言中意。初刻拍案驚奇˙卷三：老身虛心冷氣，看他眉頭眼後，常是不中意，受他凌辱的。] <br />\n<br />\n意思類似「啱聽」. <br />\n<br />\n所以要真的要寫的話, 「鍾意」比較正確. 而且「中意」的「中」讀「種」音(同「中獎」「中傷」, 「中規中距」等情況), 不是讀「鍾」音. <br />\n<br />\n2006-05-22 19:11:02 補充 <br />\n以上只適用於口語廣東話, 考試不可以真的寫「鍾意」. 而且如果是考辨認錯別字, 「鍾意」是別字,「中意」才是正確. <br />\n<br />\n來源: <a href=\"http://hk.knowledge.yahoo.com/question/question?qid=7006052201558\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.knowledge.yahoo.com%2Fquestion%2Fquestion%3Fqid%3D7006052201558&d=NcxA%2FjSO37%2BbTFwcb3mv0BpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=8390869e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.knowledge.yahoo.com/question/question?qid=7006052201558</a>"},{"pid":"c23229c8384450d5ba1dd9ffc21581e8b27d9f12","tid":58538,"uid":38449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T05:39:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n好無說服力喎<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我講話正規詞典就算唔會有呢個詞語用法, 字義都要岩<br />\n正規詞典係cross reference 字義用, 你查成個詞做乜"},{"pid":"60821c7af5c572f9662f27179366c7a7f23185b3","tid":58538,"uid":57140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T05:41:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=