> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ae2ab2e484b4afd908ae79de1044cb973f5fe0","tid":58538,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T05:45:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n好無說服力喎<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我講話正規詞典就算唔會有呢個詞語用法, 字義都要岩<br />\n正規詞典係cross reference 字義用, 你查成個詞做乜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我只係想知鍾意定中意係啱，而我搵到嘅資料都係偏向用鍾意代表喜歡。<br />\n<br />\n鍾意 = 喜歡<br />\n中意 = 滿意、合意"}]}